    FROM [Devices] AS [d]
    ORDER BY [d].[Name]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Locations] AS [l] ON [t].[LocationId] = [l].[LocationId]
INNER JOIN [DeviceTypes] AS [d0] ON [t].[DeviceTypeId] = [d0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Name]
